metadata.title: Anthony Brown & Group Therapy
description: Take Donnie McClurkin, Marvin Sapp, James Fortune & Fiya, Donald Lawrence & Richard Smallwood with a sprinkle of Kirk Franklin; shake well and you have Anthony Brown & group therAPy! Believe it or not this is no hype as Anthony Brown is a brilliant singer, songwriter, choir director and vocal arranger with writing credits for songs recorded by Maurette Brown-Clark and Stephen Hurd along with being the vocal director for BET's Celebration of Gospel for 2006 & 2007. "Testimony", the first single, is impacting radio now! Other standouts are "Deep Enough" & "Do It Again" just to name a couple.
